Package: neard
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: bluez
Description: Near Field Communication (NFC) daemon
 This package contains the neard NFC daemon
 .
 neard is an NFC system level daemon that manages NFC adapters.
 .
 neard can read and write NFC tags, and send and receive data from
 NFC peers. It supports:
  * Types 1, 2, 3 and 4 tags reading and writing.
  * SNEP (Simple NDEF Exchange Format) for exchanging data with NFC peers.
  * Bluetooth NFC Handover in both selector and requester modes.

Package: neard-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${python:Depends},
	 neard (= ${binary:Version}), python-dbus
Description: neard command line tools
 This package contains neard test scripts

Package: neard-dev
Section: devel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libglib2.0-dev (>= 2.28), libdbus-1-dev (>= 1.4)
Suggests: neard
Description: neard development files
 This package contains header file, pkgconfig support and D-Bus API
 descriptions for developing neard plugins.
